DOMAIN-SUFFIX,discord.media
IP-CIDR,162.158.0.0/16,no-resolve
# Discord Voice Gateway & STUN
IP-CIDR,162.158.0.0/16,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,199.232.0.0/16,no-resolve
